  "text": "Before settling the question of the classification of the heat flow's minimal dilation, we consider a larger class of CP semigroups. Some of the elements of this construction can be found in [CITATION_1] . Let W z , for z ∈ C, be the Weyl unitary operators associated to P and Q, given by",
